title.narrative: Accelerating Wind Power Generation in Ethiopia

description.narrative: This programme is designed with the objective of strengthening the institutional capacity of Ethiopia in the energy sector to accelerate wind power generation, including through realisation of the first Ethiopian IPP-wind auction.
